My favorite beverage is coffee because it helps me start my day with energy and focus.
I enjoy drinking coffee in the morning before work or school, especially when it is freshly
brewed and warm. I like trying different types of coffee, but I usually prefer a simple
black coffee or a latte. Coffee also gives me a moment to relax and enjoy some quiet time.
